data.description: Welcome to Villas of Escala, an exclusive single-family residence nestled in the heart of Mission Valley within the desirable gated community of Escala. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence offers 1,425 SqFt, a spacious yard with canyon views with no neighbors behind, and an open floor plan flooded with natural sunlight. Enjoy an attached two-car garage with a Tesla home charger, ensuring your electric vehicle is always ready for your next adventure. Indulge in modern luxuries including, granite kitchen countertops, sleek window shutters and new GE Profile stainless steel appliances. Elevate your space with a trendy single basin stainless steel sink and a brand-new water heater.The living room/dining area is equipped with built-in surround sound, providing an immersive audio experience for entertainment, while the primary bedroom features its own surround sound system for added convenience. For security, the property is equipped with a comprehensive security system, ensuring peace of mind for residents. Moreover, a keyless lock with touchpad entry offers convenient and secure access to the home.   Villas of Escala boasts resort-style amenities such as two resort-style pools, a fitness center, two tennis courts, a playground, and a clubhouse. But the luxury doesn't end there. Step outside and discover even more features to enhance your lifestyle. Let your furry companions roam free at our designated dog park, where they can socialize and play to their hearts' content.  Need a space to host gatherings or conferences? Look no further than our indoor/outdoor multi-person room, complete with a full kitchen both indoors and outdoors, library/den area, and plenty of BBQs to grill up your favorite dishes. And when it's time to relax and unwind, our big grassy area offers the perfect spot for picnics and outdoor activities.  Conveniently located minutes from downtown San Diego, the beach, and major freeways, this neighborhood offers urban convenience with a peaceful retreat. Nearby parks, hiking trails, green spaces, and shopping centers, including Fashion Valley Mall, provide ample opportunities for outdoor activities and retail therapy. Snap Dragon stadium, located nearby, hosts various events throughout the year, adding to the vibrant neighborhood atmosphere Experience the best of Mission Valley living at Villas of Escala, where luxury, convenience, and natural beauty converge to create the ultimate lifestyle.
